+# Phase 0284-r7 — Projects/Copilot/specialist integrated smoke report
+
+## Decision
+
+Phase 0284-r7 adds one local composition over existing surfaces. It does not
+add a Project mode to Autodoc and does not execute a remote mutation.
+
+## Integrated path
+
+```text
+newicody/projects Actions artifacts
+→ 0281 dual-artifact run assembly
+→ authoritative request + hint-only Copilot advisory
+→ validated ctx:github-advisory reference
+→ 0284-r6 portable specialist real-memory closure
+→ existing Scheduler and fake laboratory
+→ real SQL authority
+→ real OpenVINO multilingual-E5-small, 384 dimensions
+→ real Qdrant projection and reference-only recall
+→ SQL rehydration
+→ 0281 controlled Issue publication plan
+→ Projects field projection preview for the copied bundle
+```
+
+The smoke requires the authoritative candidate and validated advisory context
+to be present in the r6 specialist command. This prevents a false composition
+where the GitHub artifacts and specialist memory path are merely executed side
+by side.
+
+## ProjectV2 boundary
+
+The field preview only contains:
+
+- `Copilot`;
+- `Avis Copilot`;
+- `Route Copilot`;
+- `Confiance Copilot`;
+- `Dernière mise à jour`;
+- `Artefact`;
+- `Cycle`.
+
+It explicitly leaves `Résumé` and `Serveur` untouched. The active
+configuration and mutation adapter belong to the bundle copied into
+`newicody/projects`.
+
+## Effect boundary
+
+```text
+live_path_status: green
+live_path_uses_real_backend: true
+github_mutation_performed: false
+projectv2_mutation_performed: false
+scheduler_created: false
+scheduler_modified: false
+parallel_orchestrator_created: false
+sql_remains_authority: true
+qdrant_projection_recall_only: true
+eventbus_observation_only: true
+```
+
+`green` applies only when the injected 0284-r6 result proves the complete real
+SQL/OpenVINO/Qdrant path. Preview or incomplete memory results do not qualify.
+
+## Next step
+
+`0284-r8-specialists-laboratories-chain-closure-audit`
